com.serena.dmclient.api
Interface BulkOperator

public interface BulkOperator

Allow operations to be performed on multiple objects at once. Currently only attribute querying is supported. Instances are obtained using the DimensionsObjectFactory.getBulkOperator(List)method.

Field Summary
static int MODE_CARRYONAFTERFAIL
          If some of the suboperations within a bulk operation fail - for instance if cannot query one of 50 change docs - then whether to continue querying the remaining requests after the failure.
static int MODE_QUERYONLYUNCACHED
          Whether to hit the database to populate the attributes of objects in the list if they already have a cached value for the attribute.

getMode

int getMode()
Get the failure mode. Note that the mode is a bit-flag so the individual flags can be OR-ed together.
